<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="routine-n">routine <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ruː'tiːn/    美 /ruː'tiːn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 例行公事；惯例：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>daily routine</strong> 
日常工作</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>establish / break a routine 
确立/打破常规</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 常规节目；一套舞步 / 舞蹈动作：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>dance routine</strong> 
一套舞步</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>My morning <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ includes jogging in the park and reading newspapers over breakfast.  （2007 上海）<br />
A.drill <br />
B.action <br />
C.regulation <br />
D.routine  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. D  </p></div>